" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 03, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xfz1665702723201.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xfz1665702723201.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xfz1665702723201.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xfz1665702723201\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use the pre-V6 search sequence for libraries of global variables.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"xfz1665702723201__topic_d142373e1_d142374e1_d142375e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xfz1665702723201__p_d142376e1_d142377e1_d142378e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$OLD_LIB_PATH</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xfz1665702723201__section_y5g_gfv_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d612276e59\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xfz1665702723201__table_d17096e1_d17097e1_d17098e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Client assignment file </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS] </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xfz1665702723201__section_xq4_1gv_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d612276e105\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xfz1665702723201__p_d142385e1_d142386e1_d142387e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$OLD_LIB_PATH</span> causes an\n            application to use a search path for libraries of global variables that is more\n            compatible with the pre-V6 search path. When <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$OLD_LIB_PATH</span> is\n            present, Uniface searches for global variables in these libraries:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xfz1665702723201__ul_evn_bgv_jwb\">\n<li class=\"li\">Form library, if specified.</li>\n<li class=\"li\">SYSTEM_Library.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"note caution note_caution\" id=\"xfz1665702723201__note_u22_dgv_jwb\"><span class=\"note__title\">CAUTION:</span> <code class=\"ph codeph\">$OLD_LIB_PATH</code> should only be\n            used in a (client) runtime environment. It should never be used in an assignment file\n            which is used by the Uniface IDE.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xfz1665702723201__p_d142388e1_d142389e1_d142390e1\">When <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$OLD_LIB_PATH</span> is not\n            present, Uniface searches for global variables in the following libraries:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xfz1665702723201__ul_vx5_jgv_jwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xfz1665702723201__li_d50114e1_d50115e1_d50116e1\">SYSTEM_LIBRARY. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xfz1665702723201__li_d50117e1_d50118e1_d50119e1\">Library specified on the application shell. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xfz1665702723201__li_d50120e1_d50121e1_d50122e1\">Library specified on the form. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533708\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533708\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$OLD_LIB_PATH Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 03, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Use the pre-V6 search sequence for libraries of global variables. $OLD_LIB_PATH Defaults Assignment file: Client assignment file Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: None Description $OLD_LIB_PATH causes an application to use a search path for libraries of global variables that is more compatible with the pre-V6 search path. When $OLD_LIB_PATH is present, Uniface searches for global variables in these libraries: Form library, if specified. SYSTEM_Library. CAUTION: $OLD_LIB_PATH should only be used in a (client) runtime environment. It should never be used in an assignment file which is used by the Uniface IDE. When $OLD_LIB_PATH is not present, Uniface searches for global variables in the following libraries: SYSTEM_LIBRARY. Library specified on the application shell. Library specified on the form. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}